{"tid":438011,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"（求解答）流浪貓企喺度唔走係咩意思？","createTime":"2017-10-16T13:38:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T14:18:50.000Z","uid":34891,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"84588e083ce0158e9dd340c107716cc8531437e2","tid":438011,"uid":34891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:38:30.000Z","msg":"今日經過公園，有隻流浪貓一路都行喺我前面，好似想帶我去一個地方咁，但行行下佢就停低，阻住我行，諗住兜過佢繼續行，點知佢又郁，死都要帶喺我前面，好似想話d野比我知咁，成個畫面好靈異<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n後尾我以為佢肚餓想人餵，所以就餵左少少野比佢食，但佢食左啖就冇食，但又一路喺附近徘徊，跟住我又倒左少少水比佢飲，但佢又唔要，但又唔肯走，請問各位隻貓咁樣帶路但又乜都唔做係咩意思？<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 隻貓眼大大，幾乾淨，d毛好整齊好靚，會唔會係家貓比人棄養想搵個主人？"},{"pid":"9931654a026d78419bd4ac5e50760eebe441890d","tid":438011,"uid":70007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:40:29.000Z","msg":"佢想收你做奴才"},{"pid":"b772d307e5d9225f07486425677c3a427375a028","tid":438011,"uid":91633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:40:35.000Z","msg":"肯親你又有能力方便可養既就養都係緣份黎既"},{"pid":"a07cc499cf89fa59c1b8f941b1b3793c97ef0b9e","tid":438011,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:40:48.000Z","msg":"捉番去養囉"},{"pid":"94d1eec9f541913d4bc20c4364377c2b2a11b075","tid":438011,"uid":34891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:44:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>肯親你又有能力方便可養既就養都係緣份黎既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我屋企唔方便養，如果唔係見佢咁有靈性我都想收留佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d586234afc541e3bbe0595b04642cf1608084952","tid":438011,"uid":99863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:45:41.000Z","msg":"貓圖？"},{"pid":"b7faca64377b1a4d0a588a80300dcca00200c32b","tid":438011,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:49:11.000Z","msg":"You're the chosen one<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"016be82b4aaf991644b8b38f34590e40b9ce2a6f"